item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: In my article this time I will discuss the concept and design of minimalist house floor plan type 36. In today's been a lot of houses designed by using type 36. Especially in big cities are now mostly been using this type of reason that now land in major cities and the more narrow the population becomes too dense. Although this is now getting a little land but it does not mean you can not have a fancy house, with you choosing minimalist house design type 36, then you can have a good home and look luxurious while still small. To enhance a variety of rooms that are in the house type 36 without comply with decorating items that would memeprcempit our space, then the best solution is to play with color combinations that will affect the beauty of the interior of the home and outside the home. The Beach House is the most popular theme is the theme of the Mediterranean. Mediterranean home display indeed seem more cheerful because of the colors are applied usually pastel colors. The house exterior design models and also more relaxed and not stiff like the most. However, the nature of the building is considered to be less in accordance with Indonesian climate. Natural conditions in the countries around the Mediterranean Sea, the Mediterranean origin of the model home, with very different indeed in Indonesia. Did you know you could split a post/page up into different web pages so that it has pagination? All you have to do is type: <!--nextpage--> into the HTML editor where you would like your page breaks to appear.

item.title: Inspiration of Modern Minimalist Carport Design
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Modern minimalist carport is the exterior of the minimalist home that is currently rife used for those who desire to add value plus the dream home. Do you already have it ?? No problem for you who have the shape of a small house or large.
Carport is synonymous with the garage of the house, Build a modern minimalist carport as mandatory because the carport is increasingly popular as an alternative area for those of you who have a vehicle, use of carport is to put a car or other vehicle.
There are various materials that you can choose to design your modern minimalist carport, but need consideration in choosing the design either from the budget, time of work and form. Every material has an age limit. For example materials made of iron, will experience corrosion and rusting. In contrast to stainless steel material, this material is not easily exposed to corrosion but requires a larger budget than ordinary iron.
You can also choose a carport made from wood, because the wood has a very high aesthetic value and has a distinctive texture so that your modern minimalist carport will look more beautiful. But the weakness is the wood the longer the wood will be weathered and vulnerable to termites.
